item.title: Best money making stat to raise?
item.dc:creator: @OmidSan OmidSan
item.description:
@OmidSan wrote:

[quote=“pk4pk, post:9, topic:188054”][quote author=OmidSan link=topic=250713.msg2107556#msg2107556 date=1205466355]

Duh, as soon as you get 82 mage you can start doing good in BH. Nice, whats your cb lev… :S

Hardly, when I was on my level 68 I got owned by a bunch of level 95 maulers. I was using rune CBow because I have 86 range and I was blitzing, but it had no effect.

Then get 94 mage to barrage, and you got owned cause you went alone.
Also, you were level 68, horrible level.
Last but not least, you probably had like 1 def which makes you the easiest target to kill.
[/quote]I’m not planning on pking 'cause bounty hunter just isn’t me.[/quote]
Oh… Then just go… Idk. Skill up
